at0004.1.description: Cumulative nutritional intake within a specified interval of time, which should be explicitly defined in a template or at run-time.
at0004.1.comment: A common use case is to record the cumulative total nutritional intake from the start time of a "nutritional day" until the time of recording. The start time of the "nutritional day" will be the start time for this event – for example 06:00. It may be defined by the application or by the value recorded in the 'Nutritional day definition' element in the Protocol of this archetype.
